# Universal Watch Page Configuration Framework
## A Comprehensive System for AI-Generated High-Converting Webinar Replay/Watch Pages

---

# 1. PAGE ARCHITECTURE

## Section Sequence (Top to Bottom)

| Order | Section | Component | Strategic Purpose | Psychological Logic |
|-------|---------|-----------|-------------------|---------------------|
| 1 | **Header/Navigation** | `WatchHeader.tsx` | Brand recognition, navigation context | Establishes trust and professional credibility |
| 2 | **Video Hero** | `VideoHero.tsx` | Capture attention, deliver core content | Immediate value delivery - "I'm in the right place" |
| 3 | **Video Player** | `VideoPlayer.tsx` | Primary content delivery mechanism | The core value exchange - education + transformation preview |
| 4 | **CTA Strip** | `CTAStrip.tsx` | Conversion opportunity post-video | Strike while engaged - highest intent moment |
| 5 | **Presenter Bio** | `PresenterBio.tsx` | Build authority and trust | "Who is teaching me?" - credibility establishment |
| 6 | **Secondary CTA** | `SecondaryCTA.tsx` | Reinforced conversion opportunity | Multiple touchpoints increase conversion probability |
| 7 | **Footer** | `Footer.tsx` | Legal, contact, brand consistency | Professional closure and support access |

---

## Conversion Flow Psychology

```
ATTENTION → ENGAGEMENT → EDUCATION → CONVICTION → ACTION
    │            │            │            │          │
    ▼            ▼            ▼            ▼          ▼
  Headline    Video      Content      Presenter    CTA
  + Promise   Player     Delivery     Authority    Buttons
```

### Key Psychological Principles:

1. **Immediate Engagement** (Video Hero) - Video as focal point captures and holds attention
2. **Value-First** (Content) - Education before ask builds reciprocity
3. **Authority Building** (Presenter) - Credibility reduces skepticism
4. **Strategic Placement** (CTAs) - Multiple conversion points at high-intent moments
5. **Minimal Distraction** - Clean design keeps focus on video and action
6. **Urgency Elements** - Limited replay access creates action pressure

---

# 2. SECTION-BY-SECTION COPY FRAMEWORK

---

## 2.1 HEADER/NAVIGATION SECTION

### Structure
```
[LOGO] (Left-aligned)
[NAVIGATION] (Right-aligned, minimal)
  - "About" (optional)
  - CTA Button (primary action)
```

### Logo Placement
- Left-aligned for brand recognition
- Subtle, doesn't compete with video

### CTA Button (Header)
```
[ACTION_VERB] [OFFER_NAME]
```
**Examples:**
- "Enroll Now"
- "Get Access"
- "Join the Program"

---

## 2.2 VIDEO HERO SECTION

### Purpose
The central focus of the entire page. The video hero contains the headline, subheadline, and the video player itself.

### Headline Formula
```
[TOPIC/TRANSFORMATION] **[BOLD_KEYWORD]**
```

**Format:** Title case with strategic bold emphasis on key transformation word.

**Variables:**
- `{TOPIC}`: The subject matter (e.g., "Growth Automation", "Sales System", "Marketing")
- `{BOLD_KEYWORD}`: The aspirational word to emphasize (e.g., "Masterclass", "Blueprint", "System")

**Examples:**
- "Growth Automation **Masterclass**"
- "6-Figure Funnel **Blueprint**"
- "Automated Sales **System**"

### Subheadline Formula
```
**Discover the [NUMBER]-step [SYSTEM/METHOD] to [TRANSFORMATION_1] With a [DESIRABLE_OUTCOME] that [BENEFIT] while you [EFFORTLESS_STATE].**
```

**Variables:**
- `{NUMBER}`: Specific step count (3, 5, 7 - odd numbers convert better)
- `{SYSTEM/METHOD}`: What they're learning (System, Framework, Method, Process)
- `{TRANSFORMATION_1}`: Primary transformation (Scale Your Genius, Grow Your Business)
- `{DESIRABLE_OUTCOME}`: The tangible deliverable (6-figure funnel, automated system)
- `{BENEFIT}`: What it does (sells, converts, generates leads)
- `{EFFORTLESS_STATE}`: Passive benefit (while you sleep, without you)

**Examples:**
- "Discover the 3-step System to Scale Your Genius With a 6-figure Automated Masterclass Funnel that sells while you sleep."
- "Learn the 5-step Framework to Build Your Empire With an Automated Sales System that converts 24/7."

### CTA Button Formula (Below Video)
```
[ACTION_VERB] In [OFFER_NAME]
```
**Examples:**
- "Enroll In Genius Launch System"
- "Join The Accelerator"
- "Get Instant Access"

---

## 2.3 VIDEO PLAYER SECTION

### Video Container Pattern
```
[VIDEO_WRAPPER]
  - Responsive aspect ratio (16:9 standard)
  - Dark/neutral background to reduce eye strain
  - Prominent play button (if paused state)
  - Progress bar with scrubbing capability
  - Volume controls
  - Fullscreen option
  
[BELOW_VIDEO_STRIP]
  - Trust indicators (optional)
  - Replay duration indicator
  - "Watch now before it expires" (urgency, if applicable)
```

### Video Platform Support
```yaml
supported_platforms:
  - wistia
  - vimeo
  - youtube
  - custom_hosted
  
embed_options:
  autoplay: false  # Respect user choice
  controls: true
  fullscreen: true
  playback_speed: true  # Allow 1.5x, 2x for experienced viewers
```

### Video Behavioral Triggers
```yaml
engagement_triggers:
  - pause_at_pitch: false  # Optional - pause before CTA section
  - show_cta_overlay: true  # Show CTA at specific timestamps
  - cta_timestamps:
    - timestamp: "end"  # Show CTA at end
    - timestamp: "75%"  # Show teaser CTA at 75%
  - exit_intent_popup: true  # Capture before leaving
```

---

## 2.4 CTA STRIP SECTION

### Purpose
Immediate conversion opportunity positioned directly after or alongside the video.

### Structure
```
[CTA_BUTTON]
Primary action button - high contrast, prominent

[SUPPORTING_TEXT] (optional)
"Limited spots available" or urgency statement
```

### CTA Button Formulas
**Primary:**
```
[ACTION_VERB] [OFFER_NAME]
```
- "Enroll In Genius Launch System"
- "Join The Program"
- "Get Started Today"

**With Urgency:**
```
[ACTION_VERB] Now - [URGENCY_STATEMENT]
```
- "Enroll Now - Doors Close Friday"
- "Get Access - Limited Time Pricing"

### Visual Hierarchy
- Button: High contrast (gradient or solid primary color)
- Full-width or centered prominent placement
- Clear hover/active states
- Arrow icon for directional cue

---

## 2.5 PRESENTER/INSTRUCTOR BIO SECTION

### Purpose
Build authority, establish trust, create human connection.

### Structure
```
[LAYOUT]: Two-column (Photo | Content) or Single column (Photo above Content)

[PHOTO]
- Professional headshot
- Circular or rounded rectangle frame
- High quality, approachable expression

[NAME]
Bold, prominent

[TITLE/ROLE]
Founder & CEO of [Company]

[BIO_CONTENT]
3-4 paragraphs following the Authority Story Arc
```

### Bio Copy Formula

**Paragraph 1 - The Origin Story:**
```
After [PIVOTAL_MOMENT] when [LIFE_CHANGING_EVENT] in [YEAR], [NAME] and [TEAM_REFERENCE] have since [CREDIBILITY_METRIC].
```

**Example:**
"After his life changed when he made his first digital program sale during a sound healing back in 2017, Joe and his team have since helped clients sell $10M+ online."

**Paragraph 2 - Credibility Stack:**
```
With a background in [BACKGROUND/EXPERTISE] followed by [YEARS] years of [DOMAIN], [NAME] has [ACHIEVEMENT_1] ranging from [RANGE_LOW] to [RANGE_HIGH].
```

**Example:**
"With a background in Electrical Engineering followed by 10 years of entrepreneurship, Joe has helped launch companies ranging from startup to $20M/year."

**Paragraph 3 - Mission Statement:**
```
As [TITLE] of [COMPANY], [NAME] leads [COMMUNITY_TYPE] who are [TRANSFORMATION_ACTIVITY] as part of [HIS/HER] mission to [ASPIRATIONAL_MISSION].
```

**Example:**
"As Founder & CEO of Growth Mastery, Joe leads a community of entrepreneurs who are launching & scaling automated digital program businesses across all industries as part of his mission to liberate human genius."

### Authority Indicators to Include:
- Years of experience
- Revenue/results generated for clients
- Number of clients/students served
- Notable achievements or background
- Mission/purpose alignment

---

## 2.6 SECONDARY CTA SECTION

### Purpose
Reinforced conversion opportunity for those who scroll past the video section.

### Structure
```
[HEADLINE] (optional)
"Ready to [TRANSFORMATION]?"

[CTA_BUTTON]
Same as primary CTA or variation

[SUPPORTING_ELEMENTS]
- Trust badges
- Guarantee statement
- Contact option
```

### CTA Variations
```
Primary Style: "Enroll In [OFFER_NAME]"
Action Style: "Start Your [OUTCOME] Journey"
Urgency Style: "Claim Your Spot Now"
```

---

## 2.7 FOOTER SECTION

### Structure
```
[LOGO] (Centered or left-aligned)

[NAVIGATION_LINKS]
- Contact
- Privacy Policy
- Terms of Service

[COPYRIGHT]
© [YEAR] [COMPANY_NAME]. All rights reserved.
```

### Keep Minimal
Watch pages should have minimal footer distractions. The goal is enrollment, not exploration.

---

# 3. DESIGN SYSTEM PRINCIPLES

---

## 3.1 Color Architecture (HSL)

### Watch Page Specific Considerations
Watch pages typically use darker/neutral backgrounds around the video area to:
- Reduce eye strain during video viewing
- Create cinema-like focus on content
- Make the video player the hero element

### Primary Palette
| Token | HSL Value | Usage |
|-------|-----------|-------|
| `--primary` | `103 89% 29%` | CTAs, accent elements, links |
| `--primary-foreground` | `48 38% 97%` | Text on primary buttons |
| `--secondary` | `152 88% 15%` | Video area background, dark sections |
| `--accent` | `45 93% 58%` | Highlights, urgency indicators |

### Video Section Palette
| Token | HSL Value | Usage |
|-------|-----------|-------|
| `--video-bg` | `0 0% 8%` | Video player background (near black) |
| `--video-controls` | `0 0% 100%` | Video control icons |
| `--video-progress` | `103 89% 29%` | Progress bar fill (primary) |
| `--video-buffer` | `0 0% 30%` | Buffer indicator |

### Neutral Palette
| Token | HSL Value | Usage |
|-------|-----------|-------|
| `--background` | `48 38% 97%` | Page background (light) |
| `--background-dark` | `0 0% 12%` | Video section background |
| `--foreground` | `0 0% 12%` | Primary text on light |
| `--foreground-light` | `0 0% 95%` | Primary text on dark |
| `--muted` | `0 0% 45%` | Secondary text |

---

## 3.2 Gradients

```css
--gradient-cta: linear-gradient(135deg, hsl(103 89% 29%) 0%, hsl(120 55% 55%) 100%);
--gradient-dark: linear-gradient(180deg, hsl(0 0% 8%) 0%, hsl(0 0% 15%) 100%);
--gradient-hero: linear-gradient(180deg, hsl(48 38% 97%) 0%, hsl(145 40% 95%) 100%);
```

---

## 3.3 Typography Scale

### Watch Page Specific
Watch pages prioritize readability and minimal distraction.

```css
/* Headlines */
H1 (Video Title): text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-display font-bold
H2 (Subheadline): text-xl md:text-2xl font-normal leading-relaxed

/* Body */
Large: text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed
Regular: text-base leading-relaxed

/* Presenter */
Name: text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display font-bold
Title: text-lg text-muted-foreground
Bio: text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed

/* CTA */
Button Text: text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold
```

### Font Families
```css
--font-sans: "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
--font-display: "Poppins", "Inter", sans-serif;
```

---

## 3.4 Spacing System

### Section Padding
```css
py-8 md:py-12    /* Compact sections (header, CTA strip) */
py-16 md:py-24   /* Standard sections (presenter bio) */
py-4 md:py-8     /* Video wrapper padding */
```

### Container
```css
container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6
max-w-4xl   /* Video section content */
max-w-3xl   /* Presenter bio content */
max-w-6xl   /* Full-width video player */
```

### Video Player
```css
/* Aspect ratio container */
aspect-video  /* 16:9 ratio */
w-full
max-w-5xl mx-auto
rounded-lg overflow-hidden
```

---

## 3.5 Shadows

```css
--shadow-video: 0 20px 60px hsl(0 0% 0% / 0.4);
--shadow-cta: 0 4px 20px hsl(103 89% 29% / 0.3);
--shadow-card: 0 4px 20px hsl(0 0% 0% / 0.1);
```

---

## 3.6 Border Radius

```css
--radius: 0.75rem;
rounded-lg    /* Video player, cards */
rounded-xl    /* CTA buttons */
rounded-full  /* Presenter photo, badges */
```

---

## 3.7 Animations

### Watch Page Specific Animations
```css
@keyframes fade-in {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

@keyframes pulse-cta {
  0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
  50% { transform: scale(1.02); }
}

@keyframes glow {
  0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 20px hsl(103 89% 29% / 0.3); }
  50% { box-shadow: 0 0 40px hsl(103 89% 29% / 0.5); }
}
```

### Animation Classes
```css
.animate-fade-in { animation: fade-in 0.6s ease-out; }
.animate-pulse-cta { animation: pulse-cta 2s ease-in-out infinite; }
.animate-glow { animation: glow 3s ease-in-out infinite; }
```

---

## 3.8 Component Patterns

### Video Container Pattern
```html
<div class="relative bg-black rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-video">
  <div class="aspect-video">
    <!-- Video embed here -->
  </div>
</div>
```

### CTA Button Pattern
```html
<a href="#enroll" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 
                         rounded-xl gradient-cta text-white 
                         font-semibold text-lg shadow-cta 
                         hover:scale-105 transition-all">
  Enroll In [Offer Name]
  <svg class="w-5 h-5"><!-- Arrow icon --></svg>
</a>
```

### Presenter Card Pattern
```html
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
  <img src="..." class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full object-cover shadow-card" />
  <div class="space-y-4">
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold">[Name]</h3>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground">[Title]</p>
    <div class="prose prose-lg">[Bio paragraphs]</div>
  </div>
</div>
```

---

## 3.9 Background Patterns

### Video Section Background
```html
<section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-900 to-gray-950 py-8">
  <!-- Dark, cinematic feel for video focus -->
</section>
```

### Content Section Background
```html
<section class="bg-background py-16">
  <!-- Light, clean background for readability -->
</section>
```

---

# 4. COPYWRITING PRINCIPLES

---

## 4.1 Headline Rules

### Watch Page Headlines
- **Concise:** 2-4 words maximum for main headline
- **Bold Emphasis:** Use `**bold**` or gradient text on key transformation word
- **Topic + Format:** "[Topic] **[Format]**" (e.g., "Growth Automation **Masterclass**")

### Subheadline Rules
- **Promise Structure:** Always include transformation promise
- **Specificity:** Include numbers (3-step, 6-figure, etc.)
- **Outcome + Benefit:** What they get AND what it does for them
- **Effortless Frame:** End with passive benefit ("while you sleep", "automatically")

---

## 4.2 Body Copy Voice

### Tone for Watch Pages
- **Direct:** Get to the value quickly
- **Confident:** The content speaks for itself
- **Aspirational:** Focus on transformation potential
- **Minimal:** Less copy, more video

### Bio Copy Voice
- **Third Person:** "Joe has helped..." not "I have helped..."
- **Achievement-Focused:** Lead with results, not effort
- **Relatable:** Include human elements (origin story)
- **Mission-Aligned:** Connect personal journey to bigger purpose

---

## 4.3 CTA Optimization

### Primary CTA Formula
```
[ENROLLMENT_VERB] [IN/THE] [OFFER_NAME]
```
- "Enroll In Genius Launch System"
- "Join The Accelerator Program"
- "Get The Complete System"

### CTA Button Best Practices
- Action-oriented verbs (Enroll, Join, Get, Start)
- Include offer name for clarity
- High contrast colors
- Arrow icon for directional cue
- Hover animations for engagement

---

## 4.4 Urgency Elements (Use Sparingly)

### Authentic Urgency Patterns
```
- "Replay available for [TIMEFRAME]"
- "Special pricing ends [DATE]"
- "Limited enrollment period"
```

### Avoid
- Fake scarcity
- Countdown timers on evergreen content
- Pressure tactics that erode trust

---

# 5. CONVERSION OPTIMIZATION PATTERNS

---

## 5.1 Video-First Layout

### Above the Fold Must Include:
1. **Headline** - Clear topic identification
2. **Subheadline** - Value proposition
3. **Video Player** - At least top portion visible
4. **CTA** - Visible without scrolling (sticky or positioned)

### Video Placement Priority
```
              ┌─────────────────────────────────┐
              │         HEADLINE                │
              │       Subheadline               │
              ├─────────────────────────────────┤
              │                                 │
              │      [VIDEO PLAYER]             │
              │                                 │
              ├─────────────────────────────────┤
              │      [CTA BUTTON]               │
              └─────────────────────────────────┘
```

---

## 5.2 CTA Placement Strategy

### Multiple Conversion Points
| Location | Purpose | Priority |
|----------|---------|----------|
| Header | Immediate access for return visitors | Secondary |
| Below Video | Highest intent - just watched content | Primary |
| After Bio | Authority convinced, ready to act | Secondary |
| Floating/Sticky | Always accessible | Optional |

---

## 5.3 Trust Building Sequence

```
1. Brand Recognition (Logo/Header) → 
2. Value Delivery (Video Content) → 
3. Authority (Presenter Bio) → 
4. Action (CTA)
```

---

## 5.4 Minimal Distraction Design

### Remove/Minimize:
- Complex navigation
- Sidebars
- Related content links
- Social share buttons (in main flow)
- Comment sections (if not moderated)

### Keep Focus On:
- Video player
- CTA buttons
- Essential trust elements

---

# 6. DATA COLLECTION REQUIREMENTS

---

## Complete Variable Schema (YAML)

```yaml
# =============================================
# WATCH PAGE DATA SCHEMA
# All variables needed to generate a complete
# high-converting webinar watch/replay page
# =============================================

business:
  name: "GrowthMastery.ai"
  logo_url: "/assets/logo.png"
  contact_email: "joe@growthmastery.ai"
  
brand:
  # Colors (HSL format)
  colors:
    primary: "103 89% 29%"
    primary_foreground: "48 38% 97%"
    secondary: "152 88% 15%"
    accent: "45 93% 58%"
    background: "48 38% 97%"
    foreground: "0 0% 12%"
  
  # Typography
  fonts:
    display: "Poppins"
    body: "Inter"

video_content:
  # Video Details
  headline: "Growth Automation"
  headline_bold: "Masterclass"  # Word to emphasize
  
  subheadline: "Discover the 3-step System to Scale Your Genius With a 6-figure Automated Masterclass Funnel that sells while you sleep."
  
  # Video Embed
  video_platform: "wistia"  # wistia, vimeo, youtube, custom
  video_id: "abc123xyz"
  video_thumbnail: "/assets/video-thumb.jpg"  # Optional custom thumbnail
  video_duration: "45:00"  # For display purposes
  
  # Replay Settings (if applicable)
  is_replay: true
  replay_expires: "2025-12-31"  # null if evergreen
  replay_message: "Watch the full replay before it expires"

cta:
  # Primary CTA
  primary_text: "Enroll In Genius Launch System"
  primary_url: "https://example.com/enroll"
  
  # Secondary CTA (optional)
  secondary_text: "Schedule a Call"
  secondary_url: "https://calendly.com/..."
  
  # Urgency (optional)
  urgency_message: null  # "Limited spots available" or null
  urgency_deadline: null  # Date or null

presenter:
  name: "Joe McVeen"
  title: "Founder & CEO"
  company: "Growth Mastery"
  photo_url: "/assets/joe-headshot.jpg"
  
  bio:
    paragraph_1: "After his life changed when he made his first digital program sale during a sound healing back in 2017, Joe and his team have since helped clients sell $10M+ online."
    paragraph_2: "With a background in Electrical Engineering followed by 10 years of entrepreneurship, Joe has helped launch companies ranging from startup to $20M/year."
    paragraph_3: "As Founder & CEO of Growth Mastery, Joe leads a community of entrepreneurs who are launching & scaling automated digital program businesses across all industries as part of his mission to liberate human genius."
  
  # Authority Metrics
  credentials:
    - "$10M+ in client sales"
    - "10 years entrepreneurship"
    - "Engineering background"

footer:
  copyright_year: "2025"
  links:
    - label: "Contact"
      url: "mailto:joe@growthmastery.ai"
    - label: "Privacy Policy"
      url: "/privacy"
    - label: "Terms of Service"
      url: "/terms"

# Page Behavior
settings:
  show_header_cta: true
  sticky_cta: false  # Show floating CTA on scroll
  exit_intent_popup: false
  video_autoplay: false
```

---

