---

# 7. GENERATION CHECKLIST

When generating a watch page, ensure:

## Structure
- [ ] 7 sections in correct order
- [ ] Video player is the visual hero/focus
- [ ] Responsive design (mobile-first)
- [ ] CTA visible above the fold or immediately after video

## Copy
- [ ] Headline uses bold emphasis pattern
- [ ] Subheadline includes numbers and transformation promise
- [ ] Presenter bio follows 3-paragraph authority arc
- [ ] CTAs use action verbs + offer name

## Design
- [ ] Video area has dark/neutral background
- [ ] CTA buttons are high contrast
- [ ] Minimal navigation/distractions
- [ ] Clean, focused layout

## Conversion
- [ ] Primary CTA below video
- [ ] Header CTA for return visitors
- [ ] Secondary CTA after bio
- [ ] No competing CTAs or confusing options

## Technical
- [ ] Video embed properly configured
- [ ] CTA links functional
- [ ] Responsive video player (aspect ratio maintained)
- [ ] Fast loading (video loads efficiently)

