# 9. WATCH PAGE VS OTHER PAGE TYPES

## Key Differences from Registration Page
| Aspect | Registration Page | Watch Page |
|--------|-------------------|------------|
| Primary Goal | Capture lead info | Deliver content + enroll |
| Main Element | Form | Video player |
| Copy Volume | Medium | Minimal |
| Sections | 8-9 | 5-7 |
| Background | Can be varied | Dark around video |

## Key Differences from Enrollment Page
| Aspect | Enrollment Page | Watch Page |
|--------|-----------------|------------|
| Primary Goal | Sell/Convert | Educate then Convert |
| Main Element | Feature sections | Video player |
| Copy Volume | High | Minimal |
| Sections | 13+ | 5-7 |
| Objection Handling | Extensive | Minimal (video does it) |

